title: Vehicle grille

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a vehicle grille, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a front elevational view of a vehicle grille showing our new design;
FIG. 2 is a right side elevational view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a left side elevational view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a top plan view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a bottom plan view thereof;
FIG. 6 is an enlarged fragmentary front elevational view thereof indicated as area 6 in FIG. 1; and,
FIG. 7 is a rear elevational view thereof.
